notes: BC Lara scored 22 off a single Symcox over.
BC Lara 7th ODI hundred (career 97 matches), 100 in 83 balls.
S Chanderpaul and BC Lara 138 runs for the 2nd wicket, highest 2nd wicket partnership for West Indies in a World Cup, 3rd highest partnership for any wicket for West Indies against South Africa.
Ends South Africa's run of 10 consecutive ODI wins.

milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (509) involving teams South Africa & West Indies in ODIs
